name: The Body Pump
description: Body pump workout is what you are looking for strength training and power and may be your gate to a lean and strong body and a shredded shape body.

name: The Cardio Workout
description: Cardiovascular exercise, also known as cardio or aerobic exercise, is essential for good health.

name: The Spartan Workout
description: Spartans took pain and made it their friend. The Spartan workout exercises some major muscle groups to give you the total warrior feeling when you move.

name: The Hardcore Workout
description: Hardcore gyms can be difficult to find. Often they’re small, operate on a tiny budget and don’t do a hell of a lot of advertising.

name: The Pro Cycling
description: Want to try road cycling but not sure where to start? We’ve got you covered. Distinct from just riding around on a bike?

name: The Body Combat
description: This high-energy martial-arts inspired workout is totally non-contact and there are no complex moves to master.
